0.000000'),(91225,87959,'NMP-2007-1.2-2','EU-funded scientists have produced a groundbreaking multi-functional scanning probe microscope capable of measuring atomic-level conformational changes, energy states and forces simultaneously.','Materials\' characterisation with one scan','2015-06-30 06:14:00.000000'),(91226,92902,'ENV.2008.3.1.3.2.','An EU-funded project developed an innovative thermal process to turn waste tyres into energy and ceramic materials.','New use of waste tyres','2015-05-26 09:53:00.000000'),(91227,97739,'NMP-2008-3.4-1','Factories are complex, dynamically evolving entities composed of multiple individual yet intricately interdependent components. A Virtual Factory Framework (VFF) promises rapid facility set-up and enhanced products for major impact.','Holistic factory simulation increases competitiveness','2014-11-17 10:06:00.000000'),(91229,90882,'FP7-PEOPLE-IIF-2008','Invasive and highly resistant to treatment, metastatic cancer is one of the leading causes of death. Inhibiting key enzymes found predominantly in cancer cells can safely and effectively reduce the growth and spread of cancer.','Fight cancer by starving cancer cells','2015-06-30 05:29:00.000000'),(91231,92442,'ENV.2008.4.2.3.1.','The \'contraction and convergenceï¿½\' framework is a route towards reducing greenhouse gas emissions in order to combat climate change. Researchers have been extending and updating this framework to provide a modernised approach to global sustainability.','The new global sustainability movement','2014-12-01 17:03:00.000000'),(91233,92870,'NMP-2008-4.0-8','Small businesses that manufacture specialised production equipment will soon have an important competitive edge. EU-funded scientists are developing novel materials for enhanced performance of machine parts.','Cost-effective and high-performance machine tools','2015-06-30 05:28:00.000000'),(91234,91202,'NMP-2008-1.1-1','A greater understanding of how individual molecules behave in biological systems w