rgy-efficient and safe light urban electric vehicles (EVs).','Making electric vehicles safer and more efficient','2015-08-03 10:16:00.000000'),(166011,94604,'FP7-PEOPLE-2009-RG','Elucidating how the immune system develops in humans is central to treating or preventing infections in newborn babies.','The immune system in newborns','2015-08-03 10:17:00.000000'),(166012,110787,'SME-2013-1','New magnetic circuit technology is about to revolutionise the way electric motors are designed, providing unprecedented power density and mechanical reliability.','Gearing up for electric mobility','2015-08-03 10:18:00.000000'),(166013,106695,'HEALTH.2012.2.4.5-2','Early diagnosis of joint arthritis remains a significant problem, and prediction of disease progression and course is challenging. The identification of disease biomarkers should help in this respect.','Novel biomarkers for inflammatory disorders','2015-08-03 10:18:00.000000'),(166014,105911,'FoF.NMP.2012-7','Exploiting very hard materials in machine tools enhances durability, decreasing maintenance and repair costs and ensuring robustly reliable products of high quality. A novel laser-processing platform will support EU leadership in diamond-based tools.','Diamonds are a machine tool\'s best friend','2015-08-03 10:18:00.000000'),(166015,99344,'NMP.2010.2.4-1','Scientists have developed novel nano-structured catalysts and selective membrane materials for catalytic membrane reactors (CMRs) of great importance to the energy sector. They promise enhanced performance and sustainability at a lower cost.','Greener and cheaper chemical processes','2015-08-03 10:19:00.000000'),(166016,106759,'SSH.2012.1.3-2','EU-funded research is providing an in-depth analysis of the evolution of labour market policies, employment policies and social policies. Specifically, the project is qualitatively and quantitatively assessing the labour market position of vulnerable groups from 2000 forward.','Labour market resilience','2015-08-03 10:20:00.